examples.en: As a group, females performed better on the test than males.
Females may be more verminous than males.
Suffrage was the prerogative of white adult males.
The females are smaller and less powerful than the males.
She attended a school where there were more males than females.
For their various and bizarrely shaped plumage, males of the bird of paradise species have few rivals.
94% of the butterflies are females, and they jostle for the attention of the few males, who seem reluctant suitors.
